      <div class="tt-scroll-down">
        <a
          href="#tt-page-content"
          class="tt-scroll-down-inner tt-magnetic-item"
          data-offset="0"
        >
          <div class="tt-scrd-icon"></div>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 500 500">
            <defs>
              <path
                d="M50,250c0-110.5,89.5-200,200-200s200,89.5,200,200s-89.5,200-200,200S50,360.5,50,250"
                id="textcircle"></path>
            </defs>
            <text dy="30">
              <textPath xlink:href="#textcircle"
                >Scroll to Explore - Scroll to Explore -</textPath
              >
            </text>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="tt-page-content">
      <div class="tt-section no-padding-bottom padding-bottom-xlg-40">
        <div class="tt-section-inner tt-wrap">
          <div class="tt-row tt-lg-row-reverse">
            <div class="tt-col-lg-6 margin-bottom-20">
              <div class="tt-video ttv-portrait ttv-grayscale">
                <video
                  playsinline
                  muted
                  autoplay
                  loop
                  preload="metadata"
                  poster="/assets/vids/1200/video-3-1200.jpg"
                  class="tt-anim-zoomin"
                >
                  <source
                    src="/assets/vids/placeholder.mp4"
                    data-src="/assets/vids/1200/video-3-1200.mp4"
                    type="video/mp4"
                  />
                  <source
                    src="/assets/vids/placeholder.webm"
                    data-src="/assets/vids/1200/video-3-1200.webm"
                    type="video/webm"
                  />
                </video>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="tt-col-lg-1"></div>

            <div class="tt-col-lg-5">
              <h2 class="tt-font-alter tt-anim-fadeinup">Hello!</h2>
              <div class="text-lg tt-anim-fadeinup">
                <p>
                  I'm Mayank Raj, a professional graphic designer with a sharp
                  focus on branding, digital creatives, and visual storytelling.
                  Based in Agra, India, I bring 5 years of experience crafting
                  visuals that don't just look good — they work.
                </p>

                <p>
                  I don't believe in decoration for the sake of design. Every
                  color, layout, and visual decision I make is driven by
                  clarity, purpose, and results. Over time, I've worked with
                  local businesses, professionals, startups, and service brands,
                  helping them present themselves confidently in a competitive
                  market.
                </p>

                <p>
                  If you're looking for serious design that represents your
                  brand properly, not random templates — you're in the right
                  place. My approach is direct, practical, and focused on output
                  — not fancy design jargon.
                </p>

                <div
                  class="tt-big-round-ptn margin-top-20 margin-left-xlg-10-p"
                >
                  <a
                    href="#"
                    class="tt-big-round-ptn-holder tt-magnetic-item"
                  >
                    <div class="tt-big-round-ptn-inner">
                      Explore<br /> My Work
                    </div>
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tt-section no-padding">
        <div class="tt-section-inner">
          <div class="tt-scrolling-text-crossed">
            <div class="tt-scrolling-text-crossed-inner">
              <div
                class="tt-scrolling-text scrt-dyn-separator scrt-color-reverse"
                data-scroll-speed="5"
                data-change-direction="true"
                data-opposite-direction="true"
              >
                <div class="tt-scrt-inner">
                  <div class="tt-scrt-content">
                    No template work – every design is custom • Strong
                    understanding of Indian market aesthetics • Clean, modern,
                    and brand-focused designs
                    <span class="tt-scrt-separator">
                      <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                      >
                        <path
                          d="M13.025 1l-2.847 2.828 6.176 6.176h-16.354v3.992h16.354l-6.176 6.176 2.847 2.828 10.975-11z"
                        >
                        </path>
                      </svg>
                    </span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div
                class="tt-scrolling-text scrt-dyn-separator"
                data-scroll-speed="5"
                data-change-direction="true"
              >
                <div class="tt-scrt-inner">
                  <div class="tt-scrt-content">
                    Clear communication & on-time delivery • Design that looks
                    premium without overdoing it • 5 years of design experience
                    • I help businesses build a strong, credible, and memorable
                    presence
                    <span class="tt-scrt-separator">
                      <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                      >
                        <path
                          d="M13.025 1l-2.847 2.828 6.176 6.176h-16.354v3.992h16.354l-6.176 6.176 2.847 2.828 10.975-11z"
                        >
                        </path>
                      </svg>
                    </span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tt-section no-padding-bottom padding-bottom-xlg-80">
        <div class="tt-section-inner tt-wrap">
          <div class="tt-row">
            <div class="tt-col-xl-8">
              <div class="tt-heading tt-heading-xxxlg">
                <h3 class="tt-heading-subtitle tt-text-reveal">What I Do</h3>
                <h2 class="tt-heading-title tt-text-reveal">Services</h2>
              </div>
              <div
                class="tt-text-uppercase max-width-400 margin-left-xlg-10-p text-pretty tt-text-reveal"
              >
                Comprehensive design services to build a strong, credible, and
                memorable brand presence.
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="tt-col-xl-4 tt-align-self-end margin-top-40">
              <div
                class="tt-big-arrow tt-ba-angle-bottom-left tt-anim-fadeinup"
              >
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path
                    d="M13.025 1l-2.847 2.828 6.176 6.176h-16.354v3.992h16.354l-6.176 6.176 2.847 2.828 10.975-11z"
                  >
                  </path>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tt-section">
        <div class="tt-section-inner">
          <div
            class="tt-horizontal-accordion tt-hac-alter-hover tt-anim-fadeinup"
          >
            <!-- Digital Media -->
            <div class="tt-hac-item cursor-alter" id="digital-media">
              <div class="tt-hac-item-count"></div>
              <div class="tt-hac-item-inner">
                <div class="tt-hac-item-content">
                  <div class="tt-haci-content-top">
                    <h2 class="tt-haci-title">Digital<br /> Media</h2>
                    <div class="tt-haci-description">
                      Social Media Creatives<br />
                      Ad Creatives & Campaign Visuals<br />
                      Promotional Digital Designs<br />
                      Online Brand Communication
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="tt-haci-content-bottom">
                    <a
                      href="/services#digital-media"
                      class="tt-btn tt-btn-outline tt-magnetic-item"
                    >
                      <span data-hover="View Services">View Services</span>
                    </a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Print Media -->
            <div class="tt-hac-item cursor-alter" id="print-media">
              <div class="tt-hac-item-count"></div>
              <div class="tt-hac-item-inner">
                <div class="tt-hac-item-content">
                  <div class="tt-haci-content-top">
                    <h2 class="tt-haci-title">Print<br /> Media</h2>
                    <div class="tt-haci-description">
                      Posters, Flyers & Banners<br />
                      Visiting Cards & Stationery<br />
                      Brochures & Print Ads<br />
                      Packaging & Label Design
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="tt-haci-content-bottom">
                    <a
                      href="/services#print-media"
                      class="tt-btn tt-btn-outline tt-magnetic-item"
                    >
                      <span data-hover="View Services">View Services</span>
                    </a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Motion Graphics -->
            <div class="tt-hac-item cursor-alter" id="motion-graphics">
              <div class="tt-hac-item-count"></div>
              <div class="tt-hac-item-inner">
                <div class="tt-hac-item-content">
                  <div class="tt-haci-content-top">
                    <h2 class="tt-haci-title">Motion<br /> Graphics</h2>
                    <div class="tt-haci-description">
                      Logo & Brand Animations<br />
                      Animated Social Media Creatives<br />
                      Promotional Motion Videos<br />
                      Visual Storytelling Content
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="tt-haci-content-bottom">
                    <a
                      href="/services#motion-graphics"
                      class="tt-btn tt-btn-outline tt-magnetic-item"
                    >
                      <span data-hover="View Services">View Services</span>
                    </a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Video Editing -->
            <div class="tt-hac-item cursor-alter" id="video-editing">
              <div class="tt-hac-item-count"></div>
              <div class="tt-hac-item-inner">
                <div class="tt-hac-item-content">
                  <div class="tt-haci-content-top">
                    <h2 class="tt-haci-title">Video<br /> Editing</h2>
                    <div class="tt-haci-description">
                      Reels & Short-form Videos<br />
                      Promotional Brand Videos<br />
                      Event Highlights & Edits<br />
                      Social Media Video Content
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="tt-haci-content-bottom">
                    <a
                      href="/services#video-editing"
                      class="tt-btn tt-btn-outline tt-magnetic-item"
                    >
                      <span data-hover="View Services">View Services</span>
                    </a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Digital Marketing -->
            <div class="tt-hac-item cursor-alter" id="digital-marketing">
              <div class="tt-hac-item-count"></div>
              <div class="tt-hac-item-inner">
                <div class="tt-hac-item-content">
                  <div class="tt-haci-content-top">
                    <h2 class="tt-haci-title">Digital<br /> Marketing</h2>
                    <div class="tt-haci-description">
                      Social Media Marketing<br />
                      Paid Ads Strategy & Management<br />
                      Campaign Planning & Execution<br />
                      Online Brand Growth
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="tt-haci-content-bottom">
                    <a
                      href="/services#digital-marketing"
                      class="tt-btn tt-btn-outline tt-magnetic-item"
                    >
                      <span data-hover="View Services">View Services</span>
                    </a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tt-section padding-top-xlg-120">
        <div class="tt-section-inner tt-wrap">
          <div class="tt-row margin-bottom-40">
            <div class="tt-col-xl-8">
              <div class="tt-heading tt-heading-xxxlg no-margin">
                <h3 class="tt-heading-subtitle tt-text-reveal">Contact</h3>
                <h2 class="tt-heading-title tt-text-reveal">
                  Let's Work<br /> Together
                </h2>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div
              class="tt-col-xl-4 tt-align-self-end tt-xl-column-reverse margin-top-40"
            >
              <div
                class="max-width-600 margin-bottom-10 tt-text-uppercase text-pretty tt-text-reveal"
              >
                If you're serious about your brand image and want designs that
                actually represent your business, let's connect.
              </div>

              <div
                class="tt-big-round-ptn margin-top-30 margin-bottom-xlg-80 tt-anim-fadeinup"
              >
                <a
                  href="/contact/"
                  class="tt-big-round-ptn-holder tt-magnetic-item"
                >
                  <div class="tt-big-round-ptn-inner">
                    Start a<br /> Project
                  </div>
                </a>
              </div>

              <div class="contact-info">
                <p>
                  <strong>Email:</strong>
                  <a href="mailto:mayankrajjain.0@gmail.com"
                    >mayankrajjain.0@gmail.com</a
                  >
                </p>
                <p>
                  <strong>Phone / WhatsApp:</strong>
                  <a href="tel:+918923087566">+91 8923087566</a>
                </p>
                <p><strong>Location:</strong> Agra, India</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
